@Produces(segment="MSH", resource=org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.MessageHeader.class, extra={org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Organization.class,org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.OperationOutcome.class,org.hl7.fhir.r4.model.Bundle.class}) public class MSHParser extends AbstractSegmentParser

      Description copied from class: AbstractStructureParser
